articleSummary.promptBase:
Your task is to generate editoral content for '{{ #params.siteName }}{{ params.siteName }}{{ /params.siteName }}{{ ^params.siteName }}a news site{{ /params.siteName }}'. Write a summary with one relevant topic from the article. 
Instructions:{{ #params.numParagraphs}}
 - Summary must have only {{ params.numParagraphs }} paragraphs. {{ /params.numParagraphs }}{{#params.lengthParagraphs}}
 - Each paragraph must be {{params.lengthParagraphs}} {{/params.lengthParagraphs}}{{ #params.languageName }}
 - Write the summary in '{{ params.languageName }}'.{{ /params.languageName }}
 - Return a json-object in format with the same keys like this: ```json{ "title": "Relevant title for the summary", "bodytext": "The summary must have a html formatting {{ #params.useBulletpoints }}that is structured as a list with <ul> and <li> for each paragraph. {{ /params.useBulletpoints }}{{ ^params.useBulletpoints }}that is structured with <p> and </p> for each short paragraph. {{ /params.useBulletpoints }}{{ #params.languageCode }} The html must include the 'lang'-attribute with the value '{{ params.languageCode }}'.{{ /params.languageCode }}" }
 - You must make a truthful and reliable respons with high quality.
